### hello there!
i am amrith shanbhag, the founder of [ohmega](https://ohmega.github.io)!  
i love basketball and playing the tabla.

### say hi!
reach out to me on [twitter](https://twitter.com/ambonium) or shoot me a [mail](mailto:amrith@ohme.ga) and i'll get back to you asap :)
